div(class='row-fluid', id='contact')
  h1 Under Construction
  
  div(class='span4', id='contact-info')
    h3 Contact Us
    p 
      img(src='http://apps.rflab.co.za/rflab/images/contact.png', style='float: left; margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px;') 
      | We are available 24/7, please don't hesitate to drop us a line for inquiries or to report bugs.
    p
      strong Support: 
      a(href='mailto:support@ragingflame.co.za') support@ragingflame.co.za
      
    p
      strong General:  
      a(href='mailto:info@ragingflame.co.za') info@ragingflame.co.za
    
  div(class='span7', id='contact-form')
    form(class='form-horizontal', action='/contact', method='post')
      fieldset
        div.control-group
          label(class='control-label', for='name') URL
          div.controls
            input(class='input-xxlarge', type='text', id='name', name='name', placeholder='Your name')
          
        div.control-group
          label(class='control-label', for='email') Email
          div.controls
            input(class='input-xlarge', name='email', type='text', id='email', placeholder='Your email address')
          
        div.control-group
          label(class='control-label', for='message') Message
          div.controls
            textarea(class='input-xlarge', rows='3', id='message', name='message', placeholder='Your message...')
          
        div.form-actions
          button(type='submit', class='btn btn-primary') SEND


   